#: ../../hardware/controllers/native_instruments_traktor_kontrol_z1.md:3
msgid "Native Instruments Traktor Kontrol Z1"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/native_instruments_traktor_kontrol_z1.md:6
msgid ""
"Native Instruments Traktor Kontrol Z1 is a two-deck ultra-compact DJ "
"controller with an integrated 96 kHz / 24-bit sound card. It features stereo"
" sound output using two unbalanced RCA connectors and a standard headphone "
"(1/8\" / 3.5 mm TRS) output jack. The controller can be powered directly "
"from the USB bus or by using an external power adapter."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/native_instruments_traktor_kontrol_z1.md:8
msgid ""
"[Traktor Kontrol Z1 product page](https://www.native-"
"instruments.com/en/products/traktor/dj-controllers/traktor-kontrol-z1/)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/native_instruments_traktor_kontrol_z1.md:9
msgid ""
